No prespeed allowed.

Play with 300fps, no scouts, 100 tick. Don't be a noob, play on a proper server with anticheat.

Thanks to getwrekt for starting this project and making the first bhop room (the one after the first easy climb room) and thanks to aoki for the textures and design.

Good servers with anticheat:

Aus kz/bhop : 203.98.81.242:28015

box n' prox : 70.42.74.82:27015

akb bhop    : 1.234.22.20:27015


KNOWN BUGS:

One particle effect has a missing texture for people with lines.pcf in their cstrike/particle folder, i think, very minor and barely noticable. Should only happen to 2 - 3 people.

Might have to disable any weapon removing server addons to complete the map.
